of_arithmetic" title=3D"Fundamental theorem of arithmetic">Fundamental theo=
rem of arithmetic</a></div>
<p>Writing a number as a product of prime numbers is called a <i>prime fact=
orization</i> of the number.<sup id=3D"cite_ref-FOOTNOTELeff2000[httpsarchi=
