&amp;ndash;65]_49-0" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.or=
g/wiki/Prime_number#cite_note-FOOTNOTELeff2000[httpsarchiveorgdetailsbarron=
smathworkb00leff_0page64mode1upq22primefactorization22_64&amp;ndash;65]-49"=
><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>47<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</spa=
n></a></sup> For example:
</p>
<dl><dd><span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span clas=
