<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading3"><h3 id=3D"Integer_factorization">Inte=
ger factorization</h3></div>
<link rel=3D"mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href=3D"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r=
1320445320"><div role=3D"note" class=3D"hatnote navigation-not-searchable">=
Main article: <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Integer_factorizatio=
n" title=3D"Integer factorization">Integer factorization</a></div>
<p>Given a composite integer <span class=3D"nowrap">=E2=81=A0<span class=3D=
"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class=3D"mwe-math-mathml-i=
nline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;"><math xmlns=3D"http://=
